---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Bebop">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-background">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16">
      <a href="/" class="text-primary hover:underline text-sm">&larr; Back to home</a>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold font-serif mt-6 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-8">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none space-y-6 text-foreground leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you join our waitlist or create an account, we collect your email address and any optional profile information you provide. We also collect standard usage data such as IP addresses, browser type, and pages visited to improve the service.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use your information to operate and improve Bebop, send you product updates and early access invitations, and communicate important changes to the service. We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use essential cookies to maintain your session and preferences. We may use analytics cookies to understand how visitors interact with our site. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, though some features may not work as expected.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Data Storage & Security</h2>
        <p>Your data is stored securely using industry-standard encryption. We retain your information for as long as your account is active or as needed to provide the service. You may request deletion of your data at any time by contacting us.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We use Vercel for hosting and analytics. When you connect external platforms (Hashnode, Dev.to, Bluesky, Mastodon), we store the access tokens necessary to publish on your behalf. We do not access more data than required for the features you use.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this policy, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@bebopcms.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">hello@bebopcms.com</a>.</p>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200" />
        <p class="text-sm text-muted italic">This is a placeholder privacy policy. A full policy will be published before Bebop exits early access.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
